2. The Problem
•
•
Contracts managed manually via PDFs
Jobs scheduled outside core systems
Invoices created independently of scope
Payments and accounting disconnected from execution
Duplicate data entry
Scope loss between phases
Jobs starting without readiness
Missed revenue (tax, retainage, billing gaps)
No end-to-end traceability
This results in operational inefficiency and consistent revenue leakage.

FloorConnector delivers a connected, production-first operating system.

