9. Competitive Advantage
• • • • • •
10. Vision
• • • • • • • • • • •
System of commerce
FloorConnector is not a point solution.

It is a vertically integrated platform positioned to own the operational, financial, legal,
and commercial workflows of an underserved segment of the construction industry.

By unifying these layers into a single system, FloorConnector creates a high-retention,
multi-revenue business with long-term platform expansion potential.

•
11. Closing
FloorConnector is not a point solution.
It is a vertically integrated platform positioned to own the operational, financial, legal,
and commercial workflows of an underserved segment of the construction industry.
By unifying these layers into a single system, FloorConnector creates a high-retention,
